resource.descriptiontext:
"CUPSS is a free, easy-to-use, asset management tool for small drinking water and
                    wastewater utilities. CUPSS provides a simple, comprehensive approach based on EPA's highly
                    successful Simple Tools for Effective Performance (STEP) Guide series. Use CUPSS to help you
                    develop:

                    A record of your assets;
                    A schedule of required tasks;
                    An understanding of your financial situation;
                    A tailored asset management plan.

                    This website is designed for CUPSS users, trainers and all others involved with small drinking water
                    or wastewater utilities. "

